/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=2a3a639f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【2225 上環】警方施放多枚催淚彈，其後多部警車在警察防線後方鳴笛 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2513792761974182&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a4b328be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182</a><br />\n7.21 催淚彈在人群中爆開 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D446725156177245&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=78ab8774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245</a><br />\n7.21 無證速龍向記者舉槍 亮警棍威嚇 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D370689103642714&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=98043cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714</a><br />\n7.21 警察開槍射胡椒彈 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D320505138857250&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=b9503847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250</a><br />\n警再放催淚彈Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnew